      "rationale": "Inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, and fluid properties (viscosity, density) matched to bench test conditions within ±3% measurement uncertainty. Five operating points (3–6 L/min, 2400–3600 RPM) replicated. Gradation 2 met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
