      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulated hemolysis index (RH) compared against experimental measurements with agreement within validation uncertainty. MRL 2 requires Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "RH values from CFD compared against in-vitro hemolysis measurements at all five operating points. Mean absolute error 6.1%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty bands (±12%). Gradation 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
