    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Credibility assessment accepted at MRL 2 for Class II CPB device. Six of seven assessed factors meet required levels. Discretization error factor achieved Gradation 2 against a Gradation 3 requirement; however, the assessment team determined that the 8.3% GCI, while above the 5% threshold, remains within engineering judgment bounds for this device class and that the overall model risk is manageable given corroborating validation evidence across five operating points. Decision proceeds to Accepted.",
